cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.MM, cs.NE 

This paper deals with deep learning models for medical image analysis, which is a common topic in computer vision (cs.CV) and machine learning (cs.LG, cs.AI). The paper specifically focuses on multi-task learning (MTL) and transfer learning, which are also relevant to the sub-categories of multimedia (cs.MM) and neural networks (cs.NE).
